WEBVTT

00:00.110 --> 00:04.920
I should be able to get a few days off for Golden Week this year.

00:06.100 --> 00:11.240
I'm pretty excited because ever since I came back from America, I haven't had much of a chance to relax.

00:12.820 --> 00:16.450
All the stress of work makes it nearly impossible...

00:18.580 --> 00:21.200
I hope I can spend the time off with Takeshi.

00:22.230 --> 00:24.240
We don't have to travel or anything,

00:24.730 --> 00:26.310
we just need to be together.

00:27.610 --> 00:30.100
I just need a little peace of mind.

00:31.150 --> 00:33.380
...Am I being selfish?
